After Darkfate enters the bright room, a whooshign sound is heard and 
a door closes behind him leaving him only in what appears to be an 
endless room of white. Before long the ground begins to rumble below 
him as a humming sound is heard. Finally to Darkfates side two parts 
of the wall slide away and the room he was in goes totally black, 
however the new doorway reveals a new room, a massive room that is 
very dark however lights of pale red and blue shine all over towards 
a large command section. A huge orb revealing a completely 
holographic representation of the Earth is also in the middle of the 
room.
